name: Hostnames (multi-domain)
description: Evaluation of hostnames in case of multi-domain website.
furtherInfo: In evaluation of data from multiple hostnames you may need to use the knowledge of acceptible hostnames that may appear in the data. </br>If you have a single-hostname website, refer to another template, https://github.com/crossmasters/waaila/tree/master/app/templates/waaila-hostnames-single
